[http://permies.com/ '''Permies'''] is an active internet forum about permaculture. 

It has around 84 sub-forums on topics from [http://www.permies.com/forums/f-72/composting composting] to [http://www.permies.com/forums/f-41/farm-income farm income] and [http://www.permies.com/forums/f-42/singles permaculture singles]. 

Permies is founded and managed by Paul Wheaton, who also runs [[RichSoil.com]][http://www.richsoil.com/], a site of permaculture articles, as well as the IT forum site focused on Java programming, [http://www.coderanch.com/ CodeRanch], "A friendly place for programming greenhorns!"


